[We now have EEE confirmed in horses in Richmond and Onslow counties in North Carolina. We can expect more.

Onslow County is on the southeast coast of North Carolina. Richmond County is inland in south-central North Carolina on the border angle with South Carolina; see: http://legacy.lib.utexas.edu/maps/states/north_carolina.gif. These are 2 widely separated counties in a state with unvaccinated horses. - Mod.MHJ

